# ------------------------------
# Obsidian Vault .gitignore File
# ------------------------------

# 1. Obsidian workspace state (local UI settings)
# These files contain UI layout, open tabs, cursor positions, recent files, etc.
# They change constantly and are NOT meaningful in version control.
.obsidian/workspace
.obsidian/workspace.json

# 2. Obsidian app cache and transient files
# Automatically generated files that vary per device.
.obsidian/cache/
.obsidian/plugins/obsidian-hover-editor/data.json

# 3. Obsidian global app settings (optional)
# If you want plug-in configuration synced across devices, REMOVE these lines.
# If you prefer device-local customization, keep them ignored.
.obsidian/plugins/
.obsidian/themes/
.obsidian/
